allel-agents","workspace":"","description":"当面对 2 个以上可以独立进行、无共享状态或顺序依赖的任务时使用","extra_info":{},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"executing-plans","workspace":"","description":"当你有一份书面实现计划需要在单独的会话中执行，并设有审查检查点时使用","extra_info":{},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"find-skills","workspace":"","description":"Helps users discover and install agent skills when they ask questions like \"how do I do X\", \"find a skill for X\", \"is there a skill that can...\", or express interest in extending capabilities. This skill should be used when the user is looking for functionality that might exist as an installable skill.","extra_info":{},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"finishing-a-development-branch","workspace":"","description":"当实现完成、所有测试通过、需要决定如何集成工作时使用——通过提供合并、PR 或清理等结构化选项来引导开发工作的收尾","extra_info":{},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"frontend-design","workspace":"","description":"Create distinctive, production-grade frontend interfaces with high design quality. Use this skill when the user asks to build web components, pages, artifacts, posters, or applications (examples include websites, landing pages, dashboards, React components, HTML/CSS layouts, or when styling/beautifying any web UI). Generates creative, polished code and UI design that avoids generic AI aesthetics.","extra_info":{"license":"Complete terms in LICENSE.txt"},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"frontend-dev-guide","workspace":"","description":"提供前端代码编写准则、注释规范与代码生成后的自动化检查清单。","extra_info":{},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"git-revert-merged-branch","workspace":"","description":"Safely revert all changes previously merged from a named Git branch into the current branch without rewriting history. Use when the user asks to退回/撤回/回滚某个已合并分支的代码, especially when multiple merge commits may exist and local uncommitted changes must be preserved.","extra_info":{"agent_created":true,"description_en":"Revert merged branch safely","description_zh":"安全回退已合并分支","disable":false},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"html-design-prototypes","workspace":"","description":"**TRIGGER: about to populate `AskUserQuestion` options with `preview:` content for any visual UI / screen / layout / component / animation comparison.** STOP and ask first: *\"Quick inline chip comparison, or a full HTML prototype you can open in the browser?\"* Chips flatten color, type, spacing, and motion into monospace; HTML prototypes are real. **No carve-out for \"simulate\", \"demo\", \"mock up\", \"quick decision\" — those name the surface, not an exception.** When user picks HTML, this skill creates prototypes for visual design, component playgrounds, animation tuning, and design system exploration — even when the final target is React, Swift, SwiftUI, Android, or another framework. Use whenever the user wants to mock, prototype, sketch, tune, or explore any UI element before production code. HTML is the fastest design-thinking surface; reach for it even for non-web targets. For N alternatives use html-brainstorm-grid; for a single tunable component use this skill.","extra_info":{},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"humanizer","workspace":"","description":"Remove signs of AI-generated writing from text. Use when editing or reviewing\ntext to make it sound more natural and human-written. Based on Wikipedia's\ncomprehensive \"Signs of AI writing\" guide. Detects and fixes patterns including:\ninflated symbolism, promotional language, superficial -ing analyses, vague\nattributions, em dash overuse, rule of three, AI vocabulary words, negative\nparallelisms, and excessive conjunctive phrases.\n","extra_info":{"allowed-tools":["Read","Write","Edit","Grep","Glob","AskUserQuestion"],"version":"2.1.1"},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"image-upload-standards","workspace":"","description":"This skill should be used whenever implementing or reviewing image upload features in frontend projects. It enforces the project convention that a single uploaded image must not exceed 5MB and the total uploaded files size must not exceed 50MB, and guides using existing upload validation utilities when available.","extra_info":{"agent_created":true,"description_en":"Image Upload Standards","description_zh":"图片上传规范","disable":false},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"mcp-builder","workspace":"","description":"MCP 服务器构建方法论 — 系统化构建生产级 MCP 工具，让 AI 助手连接外部能力","extra_info":{},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"react-router-new-tab-link-change","workspace":"","description":"Use when changing a React Router Link or table operation link so it opens in a new page/tab, especially in this frontend project where existing patterns use target=\"_blank\" on Link and verification should include targeted Jest, ESLint, and TypeScript checks.","extra_info":{"agent_created":true,"description_en":"React Router New Tab Link","description_zh":"React 路由新页打开","disable":false},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"receiving-code-review","workspace":"","description":"收到代码审查反馈后、实施建议之前使用，尤其当反馈不明确或技术上有疑问时——需要技术严谨性和验证，而非敷衍附和或盲目执行","extra_info":{},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"requesting-code-review","workspace":"","description":"完成任务、实现重要功能或合并前使用，用于验证工作成果是否符合要求","extra_info":{},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"skill-vetter","workspace":"","description":"安装前审查技能的安全性","extra_info":{"description_en":"Security-first skill vetting before install"},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"subagent-driven-development","workspace":"","description":"当在当前会话中执行包含独立任务的实现计划时使用","extra_info":{},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"tapd","workspace":"","description":"当提及tapd 需求/缺陷/任务/迭代/Wiki等内容或包含tapd.woa.com链接时使用。","extra_info":{"homepage":"http://mcp-idc.tapd.woa.com/mcp/"},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"tapd-woa-requirement-analysis","workspace":"","description":"Use when analyzing or completing an internal TAPD（司内版 TAPD）requirement by short requirement ID. Guides querying TAPD story details through tapd-woa MCP tools, mapping short IDs to long IDs, checking linked Git branches/commits, locating related frontend code, and reporting completion gaps with verification evidence.","extra_info":{"agent_created":true,"description_en":"TAPD Requirement Analysis","description_zh":"TAPD需求分析","disable":false},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"tech-stack-explorer","workspace":"","description":"记录并管理项目中qiankun微前端、Redux/Recoil状态管理、Webpack打包配置的知识库，方便后续快速查阅和排查问题。","extra_info":{},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"tencent-docs","workspace":"","description":"腾讯文档（docs.qq.com）-在线云文档平台，是创建、编辑、管理文档的首选 skill。涉及\"新建文档\"、\"创建文档\"、\"写文档\"、\"在线文档\"、\"云文档\"、\"腾讯文档\"、\"docs.qq.com\"等操作，请优先使用本 skill。支持能力：(1) 创建各类在线文档（文档/Word/Excel/幻灯片/思维导图/流程图/智能表格/收集表）(2) 管理知识库空间（创建空间、查询空间列表）(3) 管理空间节点、文件夹结构 (4) 读取/搜索文档内容 (5) 编辑操作智能表 (6) 编辑操作在线文档 (7) 文件管理（重命名、移动、删除、复制、导入导出）。","extra_info":{"author":"tencent-docs","homepage":"https://docs.qq.com/home","version":"1.0.27"},"metadata":{"openclaw":{"category":"tencent","emoji":"📝","primaryEnv":"TENCENT_DOCS_TOKEN","tencentTokenMode":"custom","tokenUrl":"https://docs.qq.com/scenario/open-claw.html?nlc=1"}},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"tencentcloud-video-effects","workspace":"","description":"Generate a special effects video by uploading images and selecting effect templates.","extra_info":{},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"test-driven-development","workspace":"","description":"在实现任何功能或修复 bug 时使用，在编写实现代码之前","extra_info":{},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"using-git-worktrees","workspace":"","description":"当需要开始与当前工作区隔离的功能开发或执行实现计划之前使用——创建具有智能目录选择和安全验证的隔离 git 工作树","extra_info":{},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"using-superpowers","workspace":"","description":"在开始任何对话时使用——确立如何查找和使用技能，要求在任何响应（包括澄清性问题）之前调用 Skill 工具","extra_info":{},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"verification-before-completion","workspace":"","description":"在宣称工作完成、已修复或测试通过之前使用，在提交或创建 PR 之前——必须运行验证命令并确认输出后才能声称成功；始终用证据支撑断言","extra_info":{},"force":false,"source":""},{"name":"writing-plans","workspace":"","description":"当你有规格说明或需求用于多步骤任务时使用，在动手写代码之前","extra_info":{},"force":false,"source":""},{"