                        保存到本地
                    </button>
                    <button id="copyBtn" class="action-btn secondary">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path fill="currentColor" d="M16 1H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14h2V3h12V1zm3 4H8c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h11c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V7c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 16H8V7h11v14z"/></svg>
                        复制链接
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="history-section">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>下载记录</h2>
                <button id="clearHistoryBtn" class="clear-history-btn">清空</button>
            </div>
            <div id="historyList" class="history-list"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>提示：请确保粘贴的是抖音分享链接（以 https://v.douyin.com/ 开头）</p>
        </div>
